adqlQueryList: SELECT series(eventTimestamp, '1h'), segments.userData.mo_payment_sendrequest_finalization_responsedescription, count(*) FROM transactions WHERE application = "MobileApp" and transactionName in ("PayForMultipleAccountsEPGFinalizationServlet", "PayForMultipleAccountsPartialEPGFinalizationServlet", "PayForOthersEPGFinalizationServlet")

SELECT series(eventTimestamp, '10m'), count(*) FROM transactions WHERE application = "MobileApp" and transactionName in ("PayForMultipleAccountsEPGFinalizationServlet", "PayForMultipleAccountsPartialEPGFinalizationServlet", "PayForOthersEPGFinalizationServlet") and segments.userData.mo_payment_finalize_update_paytype IS NULL

SELECT series(eventTimestamp, '1d'), segments.errorList.errorCode, count(*) FROM transactions WHERE application = "MobileApp" and transactionName in ("PayForMultipleAccountsEPGFinalizationServlet", "PayForMultipleAccountsPartialEPGFinalizationServlet", "PayForOthersEPGFinalizationServlet")

SELECT series(eventTimestamp, '1h'), count(*) FROM transactions WHERE application = "MobileApp" and transactionName in ("PayForMultipleAccountsEPGFinalizationServlet", "PayForMultipleAccountsPartialEPGFinalizationServlet", "PayForOthersEPGFinalizationServlet") AND segments.userData.mo_payment_finalize_update_paytype is NULL
